	<AbilityDef  ParentName="RI_PsycastBase">
		<defName>RI_Ability_InternalFunction</defName>
		<label>Breathing exercise</label>
		<description>&lt;color=#64AEF5&gt;This technique is learned by the Enlightenment Realm of the Internal Pellet Initial Approach\n\n&lt;/color&gt;Qi cost：0.33/s\n\nThe Internal Pellet Initial Approachunique cultivation gong method to control the frequency of breathing and fixed movements to adjust the body posture, so that the body is in a better state to absorb the spiritual qi. \n\nThis technique can be turned on and off freely, and when it is on, it will slowly consume the Qi.</description>
